---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Points Beyond">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About</h1>
      <p>Experience and expertise in enterprise transformation</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-content">
          <h2>John Whitlock</h2>
          <p class="title">Founder & Principal Consultant</p>

          <p>
            John Whitlock is an IT strategist with over a decade of experience driving enterprise
            transformation, strategy alignment, and operational excellence within the defense,
            security, and justice sectors.
          </p>

          <p>
            Leveraging deep expertise in enterprise architecture, business analytics, and process
            improvement, John has successfully led initiatives that save millions, enhance mission
            readiness, and deliver measurable outcomes for federal agencies and organizations.
          </p>

          <h3>Areas of Expertise</h3>
          <div class="expertise">
            <span class="tag">Enterprise Architecture</span>
            <span class="tag">IT Strategy</span>
            <span class="tag">Business Analytics</span>
            <span class="tag">Process Improvement</span>
            <span class="tag">Digital Transformation</span>
            <span class="tag">Program Management</span>
          </div>

          <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-item">
              <h3>Education</h3>
              <p>
                <strong>Master of Public Policy</strong><br>
                Georgetown University
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-item">
              <h3>Clearance</h3>
              <p>Active Top Secret clearance</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="connect">
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/johnhwhitlock/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="linkedin-link">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/></svg>
              Connect on LinkedIn
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="expertise-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="expertise-grid">
        <div class="expertise-card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Enterprise Architecture</h3>
          <p>Designing scalable, mission-aligned technology frameworks that drive organizational efficiency and effectiveness.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="expertise-card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Strategy Alignment</h3>
          <p>Developing actionable roadmaps that bridge IT capabilities with business goals and mission requirements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="expertise-card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83 2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83l.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33-1.82 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2-2h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83 2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0l.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82.33H9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2 2v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83l-.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33 1.82V9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Operational Excellence</h3>
          <p>Streamlining processes to improve efficiency, reduce costs, and enhance mission readiness.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="expertise-card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Data-Driven Insights</h3>
          <p>Delivering analytics and business intelligence that enable executive-level decision-making.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="results">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Proven Track Record</h2>
      <div class="results-grid">
        <div class="result-item">
          <span class="result-number">$17M+</span>
          <span class="result-label">Saved through operational strategy improvements</span>
        </div>
        <div class="result-item">
          <span class="result-number">10+</span>
          <span class="result-label">Years of enterprise transformation experience</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="result-highlight">
        Led the consolidation effort that created the Navy's first Business Enterprise Architecture
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="accomplishments">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="accomplishments-card">
        <h2>Key Accomplishments</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Led the consolidation effort that created the Navy's first Business Enterprise Architecture</li>
          <li>Saved $17M+ through strategic operational improvements</li>
          <li>Developed actionable roadmaps aligning IT and business goals across multiple agencies</li>
          <li>Delivered data-driven insights enabling executive-level decision-making</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .page-header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e2e8f0 0%, #a78bfa 50%, #8b5cf6 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    position: relative;
  }

  .page-header p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .about {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .about-card {
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 3rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-text), var(--color-primary-light));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .title {
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .about-content > p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-content h3 {
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .expertise {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .tag {
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
  }

  .info-item h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
  }

  .info-item p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .info-item strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .connect {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
  }

  .linkedin-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0077b5 0%, #005885 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .linkedin-link:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 119, 181, 0.4);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: white;
  }

  /* Expertise Section */
  .expertise-section {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .expertise-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .expertise-card:last-child {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    max-width: 400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .expertise-card {
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .expertise-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    background: var(--color-card-hover);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15);
  }

  .card-icon {
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .expertise-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .expertise-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Results Section */
  .results {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .results h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .results-grid {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 6rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .result-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .result-number {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-light), var(--color-primary));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .result-label {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 200px;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .result-highlight {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
  }

  /* Accomplishments Section */
  .accomplishments {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .accomplishments-card {
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 3rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .accomplishments-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .accomplishments-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .accomplishments-card li {
    padding: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .accomplishments-card li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .accomplishments-card li::before {
    content: "â†’";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .about {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .about-card {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .about-content h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .expertise-section {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .expertise-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .results {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .results-grid {
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .result-number {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    .accomplishments {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .accomplishments-card {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .accomplishments-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .result-number {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .linkedin-link {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>

<style is:global>
  /* Hide LinkedIn link in footer on this page only */
  footer p:last-child,
  footer a[href*="linkedin"] {
    display: none !important;
  }
  footer p:has(a[href*="linkedin"]) {
    display: none !important;
  }
</style>
